{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"sum","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions/sum","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath リファレンス</a></b>: <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT 要素</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath 関数</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath 軸</a>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<p><code>sum</code> 関数は、与えられたノード集合内のそれぞれのノードの数値としての値を合計した数値を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">sum(<em>node-set</em> )\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"arguments","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"node-set\"><em><code>node-set</code></em></dt>\n <dd>評価されるノード集合。 このノード集合内のそれぞれのノードが <a href=\"/ja/XPath/Functions/number\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">number()</a> 関数に渡されたかのように評価され、その結果として得られた数値の合計が返される。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"returns","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>数値。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注","isH3":true,"content":"<p><em>(なし)</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"定義","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#function-sum\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XPath 1.0 4.3</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko での対応","isH3":true,"content":"<p>対応済み。</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"sum 関数は、与えられたノード集合内のそれぞれのノードの数値としての値を合計した数値を返します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"sum","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"sum","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"sum